"The head of this doll... It's missing the eyes.
It looks like they've been removed."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[22]

I feel a bit disappointed looking at the doll that
has lost its eyeballs. I thought everything was in
place, but the head of the doll, which resembles
Sakura, was missing the two eyes that should have
been there. \FF[22]\F[8]\AA[F]
"Anyway, let's try fitting it to the doll."\n<Yukine>\F[7]\AA[F]\FF[23]

"Hmm... Ah, inside my mouth... I can taste
something. And... it's vague, but I can see
something."\n<Shuo>\F[5]\AA[FF]\FF[28]

\F[3]Seeing Sakura look at "me" for the first time with
her eyes, joy overflows in my heart. At last, we
were able to restore most of Sakura's senses.
\AA[F]\FF[28]

\F[3]Seeing Sakura's smiling face filled with emotion
makes me incredibly happy. \AA[F]\FF[28]

"Yes. Because I'm really happy. Just a little bit
more to go, Sakura."\n<Yukine>\F[2]\AA[F]\FF[22]

"It's too early for thanks. Let's keep up the
effort a little longer."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[25]
